languages.text: "В клетке жрать давали. В клетке только током били. Теперь жрать нечего и бьют не только током, но и прикладами, башмаками и ножами. Хочу обратно в клетку".

"When we were in cages, we got fed. And we got zapped, but nothing else besides that. Now we aren't getting any food and on top of the zapping, there's hitting and kicking and stabbing too. I want to go back to my cage."

languages.text: “还在笼子里的时候，我们还能吃饱饭。虽然会挨电，但也就是挨电而已。可现在，我们什么吃的都没有，除了挨电，还要挨揍、挨踢、挨砍。我真想回到笼子里。”

languages.text: 「俺らが檻の中にいた頃は、食事が出た。殴られもしたけど、それ以上の事はなかった。今は食事も貰えないし、殴る以外に叩かれたり蹴られたり、刺されたりもする。もう檻の中に戻りたい」
languages.original_text: "When we were in cages, we got fed. And we got zapped, but nothing else besides that. Now we aren't getting any food and on top of the zapping, there's hitting and kicking and stabbing too. I want to go back to my cage."

languages.text: «Cuando estábamos enjaulados nos daban de comer. Nos electrocutaban, pero nada más. Ahora no nos dan de comer y además de electrocutarnos también nos pegan, nos dan patadas y nos apuñalan. Quiero irme de vuelta a mi jaula».
languages.original_text: "When we were in cages, we got fed. And we got zapped, but nothing else besides that. Now we aren't getting any food and on top of the zapping, there's hitting and kicking and stabbing too. I want to go back to my cage."

traits.locale_text: «Cuando estábamos enjaulados nos daban de comer. Nos golpeaban y nos golpeaban. Ahora no nos dan de comer y además de golpearnos también nos pegan, nos dan patadas y nos apuñalan. Quiero irme de vuelta a mi jaula».

languages.text: "Als wir in Käfigen waren, wurden wir gefüttert. Und geschockt, aber sonst nichts, nur geschockt. Jetzt kriegen wir kein Essen und zusätzlich zum Schocken gibt's noch Schlagen und Treten und Stechen. Ich will wieder in meinen Käfig."
languages.original_text: "When we were in cages, we got fed. And we got zapped, but nothing else besides that. Now we aren't getting any food and on top of the zapping, there's hitting and kicking and stabbing too. I want to go back to my cage."

traits.locale_text: "Als wir in Käfigen waren, wurden wir gefüttert. Und geschockt, aber sonst nichts, nur geschockt. Jetzt kriegen wir kein Essen und zusätzlich zum Schocken gibt's noch Schlagen und Treten und Stechen. Ich will wieder in meinen Käfig."

languages.text: « Quand on était en cage, on était nourris, au moins. Bon, c'est vrai qu'on se prenait régulièrement des décharges, mais c'était tout. Là, on a rien à manger, et en plus de se faire électrocuter, on se fait tabasser, bastonner et poignarder. Je veux retourner dans ma cage. »
languages.original_text: "When we were in cages, we got fed. And we got zapped, but nothing else besides that. Now we aren't getting any food and on top of the zapping, there's hitting and kicking and stabbing too. I want to go back to my cage."

languages.text: "Kafeslerdeyken yemeğimiz oluyordu. Şoklanıyorduk ama başka bir şey yapmıyorlardı. Şimdi hem yemeğimiz yok hem de şoklanmanın üstüne bir de yumruklanma, tekmelenme ve bıçaklanmaya maruz kalıyoruz. Ben kafesime dönmek istiyorum."
languages.original_text: "When we were in cages, we got fed. And we got zapped, but nothing else besides that. Now we aren't getting any food and on top of the zapping, there's hitting and kicking and stabbing too. I want to go back to my cage."

traits.locale_text: "Kafeslerdeyken yemeğimiz oluyordu. Şoklanıyorduk ama onun dışında başka bir şey yoktu. Şimdi hem yemeğimiz yok hem de şoklanmanın üstüne bir de yumruklanma, tekmelenme ve bıçaklanmaya maruz kalıyoruz. Ben kafesime dönmek istiyorum."
